sd=Consumer Investments	Handle the consumer front-end trading requests. These will typically be blocked/netted for market execution	An consumer initiates a securities purchase for their investment portfolio, providing funds from their linked 'trading' current account	This supports consumer initiated securities investment and trading activity for their self-managed securities investments. Trades will typically be blocked/netted against the bank's own securities position for subsequent market execution. Quotes/prices are based on the prevailing price at the time of the customer instruction to trade
sdpath=consumer-investments
crpath=consumer-securities-order-transaction
crr=Consumer Securities Order Transaction Instance
mcr=Consumer Securities Order Transaction
bqs=Quote Compliance FundingCheck OrderInitiation
CONFIG
ConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransaction	initiate	Initiate a consumer securities order		initiateConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransaction		#desc
ConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransaction	update	Update details on an active consumer securities order		updateConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransaction		#desc
ConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransaction	retrieve	Retrieve details about a consumer securities order		retrieveConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransaction		#desc
Quote	retrieve	Retrieve bank quote for a security	retrieveConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransactionQuote	retrieveConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransactionQuote		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Quote instance related report
Compliance	retrieve	Retrieve details about a consumer securities order compliance check	retrieveConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransactionCompliance	retrieveConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransactionCompliance		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Compliance instance related report
FundingCheck	retrieve	Retrieve details about a funding check for a consumer securities order	retrieveConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransactionFundingCheck	retrieveConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransactionFundingCheck		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Funding Check instance related report
OrderInitiation	exchange	Accept, reject etc. a proposed consumer securities order	exchangeConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransactionOrderInitiation	exchangeConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransactionOrderInitiation		Handle an external exchange (e.g. accept, reject, verify)
OrderInitiation	retrieve	Retrieve details about a consumer securities order	retrieveConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransactionOrderInitiation	retrieveConsumerSecuritiesOrderTransactionOrderInitiation		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Order Initiation instance related report
